{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"A Blog","author":"Scott Williams"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c46daa53-304f-5579-8d98-f744ef7ba2f0","excerpt":"","html":"<div><div><div><div><div>\n<div>On people underestimating the power of exponential growth:</div>\n<p></p>\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8ex; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-left-style: solid; padding-left: 1ex;\"> \"If a uranium nucleus emits two neutrons, both of which collide with other uranium nuclei, causing them to emit two neutrons, and so forth—well, did I mention nuclear holocaust as a possible end to population growth?\"</blockquote> <p></p>\n<div>Scott Aaronson in <a href=\"http://www.scottaaronson.com/writings/bignumbers.html\">\"Big Numbers\"</a>. Found via <a href=\"http://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=1539538\">Hacker News</a>.</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Nice Writing: Big Numbers","date":"July 22, 2010"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2010/07/22/nice-writing-big-numbers/index.html/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2010/07/21/insanely-useful-photo-reference-on-the-iphone/index.html/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Insanely Useful Photo Reference on the iPhone"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2010/07/22/actually-aim-no/index.html/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Actually AIM, No"}}}}